704879f-c.title: Brooklyn: Herkimer Street - Schenectady Avenue
704879f-c.text:
633 to 643 Herkimer Street, north side, east of Schenectady
Avenue. No. 633 is the Brown Memorial Baptist Church and No. 635
is the parish house.
Vew 1 September 12, 1940
P. L. Sperr  Vew 2 a  0-SP 27, F9r
NO REPRODCTIONS
Ca.. 3; 2  2~ 67, 3V7
